review_data.title: Casual take away food
review_data.content: Convenience is the key here. We got snacks and beverages at decent prices. We found the delivery prompt and professional service.

review_data.title: A Swiss Gourmet Delight at Departure Gates of International Airports
review_data.content: We noticed a good addition of well presented breakfast delicacies and beverages at the Gourmet stall at Berlin airport for our flight to London. The coffee was good, better than most airports. Well done
